@startuml order_states
!include ../theme.iuml

title Životní cyklus agregátu Order – stavové přechody

[*] --> Draft : place(items)
Draft --> Paid : pay(payment)
Draft --> Cancelled : cancel(reason)

Paid --> Shipped : ship(shipmentId)
Paid --> Refunded : refund(reason)

Shipped --> Delivered : confirmDelivery()
Shipped --> Returned : returnRequest()

Returned --> Refunded : approveRefund()

Delivered --> [*]
Cancelled --> [*]
Refunded --> [*]

note right of Draft
  Invariant: alespoň
  jedna položka.
end note

note right of Paid
  Invariant: payment.amount
  == sum(items).
end note

note bottom of Cancelled
  Cancel jen z Draft.
  Po Paid je nutný refund,
  ne cancel.
end note

note bottom of Shipped
  Po Shipped není
  cesta zpět do Paid.
  Vrácení = oddělený
  stav Returned.
end note

@enduml
